lass=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n難戒過打j"},{"pid":"806012695e9c4a169a37c6452e2c03bb5987a82b","tid":491651,"uid":79442,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-11T16:17:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/07/011226_be6b7ad666e31f466ca3510cb7289dde.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F07%2F011226_be6b7ad666e31f466ca3510cb7289dde.jpg&h=6b24be03&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n圖解哲學"},{"pid":"fad564fb69dcd4649e5885b6f0718fb35a61aa9d","tid":491651,"uid":108467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-11T16:19:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>成聖丶成仙丶成佛丶成人 - 正視人的高貴與醜惡</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/12/001920_197016a96c4462724744a8048aa9df87.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F12%2F001920_197016a96c4462724744a8048aa9df87.jpg&h=fa355842&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n作者簡介<br />\n<br />\n溫偉耀，早年在香港中文大學攻讀物理學，以量子力學研究取得碩士學位。然後轉為研究哲學及宗教學，先後再拿了兩個博士學位：一個是英國牛津大學的哲學博士，專攻現代西方哲學及基督教神學；另一個是香港中文大學的哲學博士，專攻中國哲學。1999年起任教於香港中文大學文化及宗教研究系，並兼任漢語基督教文化研究所莫慶堯醫生傑出神學教授、加拿大多倫多大學亞洲神學中心研究員。溫教授近年致力參與中國學術界對基督教的研究及教學，並被邀擔任中國人民大學、浙江大學、武漢大學、山東大學、四川大學等七所大學的客座教授。"},{"pid":"017108f12eee3566718bf0b9e30547204e2b3cdd","tid":491651,"uid":22604,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-11T16:45:15.000Z","msg":"Peter Singer - The Most Good You Can Do"},{"pid":"cc85f3252eaa61636df0be15d84e1b7e8b527984","tid":491651,"uid":134865,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-11T17:40:13.000Z","msg":"the grand chessboard<br />\n戰爭論"},{"pid":"fc87217f2caf75994bcee900adecc76abe1ce709","tid":491651,"uid":3302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-11T17:41:04.000Z","msg":"老夫子"},{"pid":"afe9b90f3dfff90b0ab28cb795e0f69f70b4aa6b","tid":491651,"uid":155354,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy